    public class TableFilterQueryJPanel
extends AbstractFilterQueryJPanel
implements java.io.Serializable
    This class is the graphical interface of the "FilterDialog" which was made by Fernando and is in 'appgvSIG' project. It's supposed that other classes will extend from this and will add the logic as is in the "FilterDialog" class.
